A rough plan of what we plan to add and in which version.
This can (and is likely to) change.

  Important - 1.2.x (User-centric) -

    Floating (parallel to main releases) -
        Redo install to be interactive.
        Tests (unit, ajax and javascript).

    1.2.6 -
        Refactor.
        Unit tests.
        Theme chooser.
        Add xml file to each template to give standard info (Creator, version, etc).
        Slide Show.

    1.2.7 -
        Provide friendly URL rewriting. (Via HTAccess)
        Image Filenames should be what they are originally uploaded as for SEO.
        Split options page up.
        On template change need to be able to regenerate thumbnails.
        Path checks in settings should AJAX check to see if they are real.

    1.2.8 -
        Cache scaled image.
        Search (with option to make new gallery from results).
        Filmstrip.
        Mobile template
        Final 1.2.x bug check.

    1.3.0 -
        Image/gallery manager on admin pages.
        Re-Arrange images on a gallery via the admin manager.
        User-defined thumbnails on galleries.
        Drop down menu from breadcrumbs showing sub-galleries for direct navigation.
        Move user/tag admin to image/gallery manager system.


    1.3 series (Expanding content) -
        Automated update from moagallery.net.
        Display movie clips.
        Grab and save EXIF info.
        Simple edit ability. (crop, resize, rotate, etc)
        IPTC support
	      Add a custom error handling page.
        GeoTagging support. (Google maps, Live maps, etc embeddable)
        Expand web API to be useful outside of the Moa frontend - to allow the client app.
        Mass Image Tagging.
        Bulk Delete.
        Gallery Merge.
        Move Sub Gallery. (Base on version of navigation bar as an admin page)

    2.0 -
        Support other databases (ms-sql, Oracle, ProgresSQL, etc) and HTTP backends (IIS).
        Import/Export (With desktop client)
        Output slideshow to Vid-CD (Online \ Desktop Client)


   Patch (Can be added at any point, sooner rather than later if poss) -
       Move all strings into a language array.
       Recently added images.
       Try different sized images to test for the jpeg decoder overhead.
       Add more corruption detection in the admin section (Look for images that can't exist in any gallery)
       Image Integrity->no image/thumb needs to have a delete option.
       Add sub-gallery, changing parent doesn't update tags (confirm box - do you want to set tags to be the same?).
       Implement a image storage quota system for Moa.
       Images with no main image should show thumbnail on the 'fix' screen.
       Boolean Tag Operators for galleries.
       Copy tags from other gallery.
       On delete tag, check if any images/galleries use that tag.
       Correct time for timezone.
       robots.txt.
       Resize pics on upload.
       Watermark/Logo stamp on pics.
       Replace image.
       User action logging.
       On maintain image, redirect back to maintain image when new image added.
       Javascript generated globals should be passed into the constructors.
       Option to unmask password boxes.
       Audio caption.